company-info: 3M Company is an American multinational conglomerate corporation operating in the fields of industry, worker safety, US health care, and consumer goods.

Alphabet Inc. is an American multinational conglomerate that was created through a corporate restructuring of Google on October 2, 2015.
Amazon.com, Inc. is an American multinational technology company based in Seattle, Washington, which focuses on e-commerce, cloud computing, digital streaming, and artificial intelligence.
